$ Oracle Active Data Guard vs Golden Gate

table { ll

 ~Active → development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard[Data Guard]~ ☰ ~→ development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Golden-Gate[Golden Gate]~
  Best protection for Oracle databases only ☰ Heterogeneous source- and target databases, versions, data structures, plattfomrs
  Fast failover in case of emergency ☰ 
  Standby database read only ☰ All databases can be written to

